highlights.text: “Kumkumala (From "Brahmastra (Telugu)")” by Pritam and Sid Sriram is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hyderabad, up 34 spots at #21.
“Veyyinokka” by Ilaiyaraaja, Harshavardhan Rameshwar, and Anurag Kulkarni is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hyderabad at #19.
Sid Sriram has the most spots on Top Songs Hyderabad. “Urike Urike” is the highest at #5.
“Gundellonaa (From "Ori Devuda")” by Anirudh Ravichander, Leon James, and Kasarla Shyam has been on Top Songs Hyderabad the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
